a.n: Agent Binky: Pets of the Universe I (22)

p.k: Unidentified FUN Object When Gordon accidentally throws Small Human’s training disc (Frisbee) over the fence, the team goes on a mission in deep space to retrieve it.
p.d: Binky is an indoor cat who is a member of a secret agency. Teamed with like-minded pet agents, they are on a mission to keep their humans and "space station" safe from "aliens".
